---
const pillars = [
  {
    title: 'Systems, not just traffic',
    body: 'A website is not a brochure. Channels are not a checklist. We build the full system that converts attention into revenue, and engineer it to keep working without you.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Marketing built for AI search',
    body: 'Prospects already ask ChatGPT, Perplexity, and Gemini before they ever see Google. We make sure those models recommend you, with our Generative Engine Optimization approach.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Automation as a multiplier',
    body: 'AI workflows replace the manual lag between lead, follow-up, and close. The same team handles 3x the volume, with cleaner data and faster response times.',
  },
  {
    title: 'Conversion before traffic',
    body: 'Traffic without conversion is theatre. We measure outcomes that move revenue: booked calls, qualified leads, closed deals, lifetime value.',
  },
];
---

<section id="why" class="relative bg-black py-24 text-white md:py-36">
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 bg-grid-dark opacity-50 [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,black_20%,transparent_70%)]"></div>
  <div class="pointer-events-none absolute -left-32 top-1/3 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-gold/10 blur-3xl"></div>

  <div class="container-x relative">
    <div class="max-w-3xl">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-gold-soft">
        <span class="h-px w-6 bg-gold-soft"></span>
        Why Rumeira
      </span>
      <h2 class="mt-5 font-display text-4xl font-medium leading-[1.05] tracking-tight md:text-6xl">
        Most agencies sell pieces.<br/>
        <span class="text-white/45">We build the engine.</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-6 max-w-2xl text-lg text-white/65">
        We integrate marketing, web, and AI so they reinforce each other. The result is a measurable, repeatable growth system, not a stack of disconnected campaigns.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 grid gap-px overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-white/10 bg-white/10 md:grid-cols-2">
      {pillars.map((p, i) => (
        <div class="bg-black p-8 transition-colors duration-500 hover:bg-white/[0.02] md:p-12">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 text-gold-soft">
            <span class="font-display text-sm">0{i + 1}</span>
            <span class="h-px w-8 bg-gold-soft/60"></span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="mt-6 font-display text-2xl font-medium leading-tight md:text-3xl">
            {p.title}
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-4 max-w-md text-sm leading-relaxed text-white/60 md:text-base">
            {p.body}
          </p>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
